  <entry>
    <title>计算几何</title>
    <link href="/2021/02/16/%E8%AE%A1%E7%AE%97%E5%87%A0%E4%BD%95/"/>
    <url>/2021/02/16/%E8%AE%A1%E7%AE%97%E5%87%A0%E4%BD%95/</url>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h1 id="计算几何（二维）"><a href="#计算几何（二维）" class="headerlink" title="计算几何（二维）"></a>计算几何（二维）</h1><p>今天我主要要和大家讨论的是计算几何。</p><p>然后因为篇幅和时间问题，今天主要是讲一下基础的东西。让大家对计算几何有所了解。</p><h2 id="前言"><a href="#前言" class="headerlink" title="前言"></a>前言</h2><p>计算几何主要是 板子+思维。</p><p>计算几何的很多题目不会说特别难，主要是费工夫。<br><del>当你把该做的题都做完了，就可以开计算几何了（暴论）</del></p><p>板子一般都会提前准备好，并且你一定一定要好好验证板子的正确性，避免边界问题或者假的复杂度。<br>各大oj都有相应的题目，可以自己去找找。<br><strong>(ps：曾经某人因其Millar_rabin板子疯狂出锅成为了ccpc区域赛某负一队锅王)</strong></p><p>思维就要靠训练提升，然后很多知识能和高中数学、数学竞赛的数学以及高数能联系起来。</p><p>然后板子和知识面还是挺广的。因为讲课时间问题 <del>（其实是懒）</del>，我只做了前一小部分。<br><strong>（dbq QAQ）</strong><br>之后我会慢慢做完，从博客里面完善，以及会在群里发pdf和cpp的压缩包。</p><h2 id="前置知识"><a href="#前置知识" class="headerlink" title="前置知识"></a>前置知识</h2><h3 id="常用常数"><a href="#常用常数" class="headerlink" title="常用常数"></a>常用常数</h3><p>我们由 $cos(\pi)=-1.0$ 可以知道 $\pi=arccos(-1.0)$。<br>$arccos(x)$ 是 $cos(x)$ 的反函数。<br>在cpp里面，使用 acos 表示 $arccos$。</p><p>而大部分计算几何题目是 spj ，会根据你的答案的精度进行判断。<br>我们计算几何的很多函数都要用到 eps 即 $\varepsilon$。<br>eps 是小数点后多少位一般根据题目判断。</p><figure class="highlight cpp"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs cpp"><span class="hljs-keyword">const</span> <span class="hljs-keyword">double</span> Pi = <span class="hljs-built_in">acos</span>(<span class="hljs-number">-1.0</span>);<br><br><span class="hljs-keyword">const</span> <span class="hljs-keyword">double</span> eps = <span class="hljs-number">1e-10</span>;<span class="hljs-comment">//1e-n,n根据题目要求;</span><br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="弧度角度变换"><a href="#弧度角度变换" class="headerlink" title="弧度角度变换"></a>弧度角度变换</h3><p>$180^\circ == \pi (rad)$</p><figure class="highlight cpp"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs cpp"><span class="hljs-function"><span class="hljs-keyword">double</span> <span class="hljs-title">R_to_Angle</span><span class="hljs-params">(<span class="hljs-keyword">double</span> rad)</span><span class="hljs-comment">//弧度转角度</span></span><br><span class="hljs-function"></span>&#123;<span class="hljs-keyword">return</span> <span class="hljs-number">180</span> / Pi * rad;&#125;<br><br><span class="hljs-function"><span class="hljs-keyword">double</span> <span class="hljs-title">Angle_to_R</span><span class="hljs-params">(<span class="hljs-keyword">double</span> angle)</span><span class="hljs-comment">//角度转弧度</span></span><br><span class="hljs-function"></span>&#123;<span class="hljs-keyword">return</span> Pi / <span class="hljs-number">180</span> * angle;&#125;<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="三态函数"><a href="#三态函数" class="headerlink" title="三态函数"></a>三态函数</h3><p>先说一下，尽管<strong>double</strong>能存下$1.79769*10^{308}$这么大的数,但是<strong>double</strong>的有效数字是有限的，大概是$15、16$位。<br>而且很多运算会损失精度。<br>很多时候我们判断一个数的符号或者判断两个数相等因为精度问题就不那么方便。所以，我们引进三态函数即符号函数。<br>（有些毒瘤的题目还要求使用<strong>long double</strong>）</p><figure class="highlight cpp"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs cpp"><span class="hljs-function"><span class="hljs-keyword">int</span> <span class="hljs-title">sgn</span><span class="hljs-params">(<span class="hljs-keyword">double</span> x)</span></span><br><span class="hljs-function"></span>&#123;<br>    <span class="hljs-keyword">if</span>(<span class="hljs-built_in">fabs</span>(x) &lt; eps)<span class="hljs-comment">//fabs是浮点数的绝对值函数</span><br>        <span class="hljs-keyword">return</span> <span class="hljs-number">0</span>;<span class="hljs-comment">//等于0的情况</span><br>    <span class="hljs-keyword">if</span>(x &lt; <span class="hljs-number">0</span>)<br>        <span class="hljs-keyword">return</span> <span class="hljs-number">-1</span>;<span class="hljs-comment">//小于0的情况</span><br>    <span class="hljs-keyword">return</span> <span class="hljs-number">1</span>;<span class="hljs-comment">//最后只剩下大于0的情况</span><br>&#125;<br><span class="hljs-comment">//判断两个数相等只需要两个数作差看sgn是否为0</span><br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>看到这里，其实计算几何很简单，对吧。</p><h2 id="表示与运算"><a href="#表示与运算" class="headerlink" title="表示与运算"></a>表示与运算</h2><h3 id="点和向量"><a href="#点和向量" class="headerlink" title="点和向量"></a>点和向量</h3><h4 id="基本运算"><a href="#基本运算" class="headerlink" title="基本运算"></a>基本运算</h4><p>如图，A，B，C为点，<strong>AC</strong>和<strong>AB</strong>为向量。<br>在二维计算几何中，向量和点都由两个<strong>double</strong>确定。</p><p>我们重点要讲的是内积（点乘）和向量积（叉乘），这两个很重要。</p><p>其中内积运算规则如下：<br>$\alpha \cdot \beta=|\alpha||\beta|cos\theta$<br>物理意义是向量$\alpha$在向量$\beta$上的投影。（或者$\beta$在$\alpha$上的投影）<br>但我们只需要这个数值就可以了。</p><p>向量积运算规则如下：<br>$\alpha \times \beta=|\alpha||\beta|sin\theta$<br>注意：向量积对向量有次序。<br>$\theta$是由向量$\alpha$旋转到向量$\beta$的夹角。<br>（和物理上不一样，物理中向量积的意义应该是向量）<br>我们也是只要这个数值。hhh</p><p>它俩能做很多事情。</p><figure class="highlight cpp"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br><span class="line">21</span><br><span class="line">22</span><br><span class="line">23</span><br><span class="line">24</span><br><span class="line">25</span><br><span class="line">26</span><br><span class="line">27</span><br><span class="line">28</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs cpp"><span class="hljs-meta">#<span class="hljs-meta-keyword">include</span><span class="hljs-meta-string">&lt;bits/stdc++.h&gt;</span></span><br><span class="hljs-keyword">using</span> <span class="hljs-keyword">namespace</span> <span class="hljs-built_in">std</span>;<br><span class="hljs-class"><span class="hljs-keyword">struct</span> <span class="hljs-title">Point</span></span><br><span class="hljs-class">&#123;</span><br>    <span class="hljs-keyword">double</span> x, y;<br>    Point(<span class="hljs-keyword">double</span> x = <span class="hljs-number">0</span>, <span class="hljs-keyword">double</span> y = <span class="hljs-number">0</span>):x(x),y(y)&#123; &#125;<span class="hljs-comment">//构造函数</span><br>&#125;;<br><span class="hljs-comment">//注意区分点和向量</span><br><span class="hljs-keyword">typedef</span> Point Vector;<br><span class="hljs-comment">//我们研究的是自由向量，所以只需要原点和向量的终点即可</span><br><span class="hljs-comment">//向量 + 向量 = 向量，点 + 向量 = 向量</span><br>Vector <span class="hljs-keyword">operator</span> + (Vector A, Vector B)&#123;<span class="hljs-keyword">return</span> Vector(A.x + B.x, A.y + B.y);&#125;<br><span class="hljs-comment">//点 - 点 = 向量(向量BC = C - B)</span><br>Vector <span class="hljs-keyword">operator</span> - (Point A, Point B)&#123;<span class="hljs-keyword">return</span> Vector(A.x - B.x, A.y - B.y);&#125;<br><span class="hljs-comment">//向量 * 数 = 向量</span><br>Vector <span class="hljs-keyword">operator</span> * (Vector A, <span class="hljs-keyword">double</span> p)&#123;<span class="hljs-keyword">return</span> Vector(A.x * p, A.y * p);&#125;<br><span class="hljs-comment">//向量 / 数 = 向量</span><br>Vector <span class="hljs-keyword">operator</span> / (Vector A, <span class="hljs-keyword">double</span> p)&#123;<span class="hljs-keyword">return</span> Vector(A.x / p, A.y / p);&#125;<br><br><span class="hljs-comment">//向量 * 向量 = 数</span><br><span class="hljs-function"><span class="hljs-keyword">double</span> <span class="hljs-title">Dot</span><span class="hljs-params">(Vector A, Vector B)</span></span>&#123;<span class="hljs-keyword">return</span> A.x * B.x + A.y * B.y;&#125;<br><span class="hljs-comment">//向量 x 向量 = 数(尽管在物理意义上应该是向量)</span><br><span class="hljs-function"><span class="hljs-keyword">double</span> <span class="hljs-title">Cross</span><span class="hljs-params">(Vector A, Vector B)</span></span>&#123;<span class="hljs-keyword">return</span> A.x * B.y - B.x * A.y;&#125;<br><br><span class="hljs-function"><span class="hljs-keyword">int</span> <span class="hljs-title">main</span><span class="hljs-params">()</span></span><br><span class="hljs-function"></span>&#123;<br><span class="hljs-keyword">return</span> <span class="hljs-number">0</span>;<br>&#125;<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h4 id="一些函数"><a href="#一些函数" class="headerlink" title="一些函数"></a>一些函数</h4><h5 id="判断逆时针"><a href="#判断逆时针" class="headerlink" title="判断逆时针"></a>判断逆时针</h5><p>因为在向量积结果中有$sin$这个函数，而且符号仅由它决定。<br>根据其性质我们可以判断向量<strong>bc</strong>是不是向量<strong>ab</strong>的逆时针方向。<br>这个函数在构造凸包的时候往往会用。</p><figure class="highlight cpp"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs cpp"><span class="hljs-function"><span class="hljs-keyword">bool</span> <span class="hljs-title">ToLeftTest</span><span class="hljs-params">(Point A, Point B, Point C)</span></span><br><span class="hljs-function"></span>&#123;<br>    <span class="hljs-keyword">return</span> Cross(B - A, C - B) &gt; <span class="hljs-number">0</span>;<br>&#125;<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h5 id="取模长（长度）"><a href="#取模长（长度）" class="headerlink" title="取模长（长度）"></a>取模长（长度）</h5><p>这个就是求两点之间的距离，这里使用的内积。<br>或者直接用两点距离公式$\sqrt {(x_1-x_2)^2+(y_1-y_2)^2}$ 。</p><figure class="highlight cpp"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs cpp"><span class="hljs-function"><span class="hljs-keyword">double</span> <span class="hljs-title">distance</span><span class="hljs-params">(Vector A)</span></span>&#123;<span class="hljs-keyword">return</span> <span class="hljs-built_in">sqrt</span>(Dot(A, A));&#125;<br><span class="hljs-comment">//double distance(Point A,Point B)&#123;return sqrt((A.x-B.x)*(A.x-B.x)+(A.y-B.y)*(A.y-B.y));&#125;</span><br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h5 id="两个向量构成的三角形面积或者平行四边形面积"><a href="#两个向量构成的三角形面积或者平行四边形面积" class="headerlink" title="两个向量构成的三角形面积或者平行四边形面积"></a>两个向量构成的三角形面积或者平行四边形面积</h5><p>根据正弦定理的推论我们有:<br>三角形abc面积=$|a||b|sinC$或者$|b||c|sinA$或者$|a||c|sinB$<br>发现正好和我们所定义向量积的形式对应。<br>平行四边形根据对称，面积正好是三角形的两倍。</p><figure class="highlight cpp"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs cpp"><span class="hljs-function"><span class="hljs-keyword">double</span> <span class="hljs-title">Area</span><span class="hljs-params">(Point A, Point B, Point C)</span></span>&#123;<span class="hljs-keyword">return</span> Cross(B - A, C - A)/<span class="hljs-number">2.0</span>;&#125;<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h5 id="向量的逆时针旋转"><a href="#向量的逆时针旋转" class="headerlink" title="向量的逆时针旋转"></a>向量的逆时针旋转</h5><p>我们有公式：<br>$x^{‘}=xcos\theta−ysin\theta$<br>$y^{‘}=xsin\theta+ycos\theta$</p><figure class="highlight cpp"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs cpp"><span class="hljs-comment">//x&#x27; = xcosa - ysina, y&#x27; = xsina + ycosa</span><br><span class="hljs-comment">//rad:弧度 且为逆时针旋转的角</span><br><span class="hljs-function">Vector <span class="hljs-title">Rotate</span><span class="hljs-params">(Vector A, <span class="hljs-keyword">double</span> rad)</span></span><br><span class="hljs-function"></span>&#123;<br>    <span class="hljs-keyword">return</span> Vector(A.x * <span class="hljs-built_in">cos</span>(rad) - A.y * <span class="hljs-built_in">sin</span>(rad), A.x * <span class="hljs-built_in">sin</span>(rad) + A.y * <span class="hljs-built_in">cos</span>(rad));<br>&#125;<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h5 id="点对于点的对称点"><a href="#点对于点的对称点" class="headerlink" title="点对于点的对称点"></a>点对于点的对称点</h5><p>很简单鸭，使用中点坐标解方程就可以了。</p><figure class="highlight cpp"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs cpp"><span class="hljs-function">point <span class="hljs-title">PdisQ</span><span class="hljs-params">(point A,point B)</span><span class="hljs-comment">//B关于A的对称点</span></span><br><span class="hljs-function"></span>&#123;<br>    point S;<br>    S.x = <span class="hljs-number">2</span> * A.x - B.x;<br>    S.y = <span class="hljs-number">2</span> * A.y - B.y;<br>    <span class="hljs-keyword">return</span> S;<br>&#125; <br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="直线和线段"><a href="#直线和线段" class="headerlink" title="直线和线段"></a>直线和线段</h3><p><span id="直线定义"></span></p><h4 id="直线定义"><a href="#直线定义" class="headerlink" title="直线定义"></a>直线定义</h4><p>由于斜率不能不存在等问题。<br>我们可以使用一般式或者点向式来表示直线。<br>一般题目给你直线是使用两个点的形式，点向式的话求一下向量就vans了。<br>然后求一般式$Ax+By+C=0$有个公式。<br>$A=y_2-y_1$<br>$B=x_1-x_2$<br>$C=x_2 * y_1 - x_1 * y_2$<br>如代码所示：</p><figure class="highlight cpp"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs cpp"><span class="hljs-class"><span class="hljs-keyword">struct</span> <span class="hljs-title">Line</span></span><br><span class="hljs-class">&#123;</span><br>    Vector v;<br>    Point p;<br>    <span class="hljs-keyword">double</span> A,B,C;<br>    Line(Vector v = Point() , Point p = Point()):v(v), p(p) &#123; &#125;<br>    <span class="hljs-function">Point <span class="hljs-title">get_point_in_line</span><span class="hljs-params">(<span class="hljs-keyword">double</span> t)</span></span><br><span class="hljs-function">    </span>&#123;<span class="hljs-comment">//返回直线上一点P = v + (p - v)*t</span><br>        <span class="hljs-keyword">return</span> v + (p - v) * t;<br>    &#125;<br>&#125;;<br><span class="hljs-comment">//求一般式</span><br><span class="hljs-function">Line <span class="hljs-title">getLineABC</span><span class="hljs-params">(Point P1, Point P2)</span></span><br><span class="hljs-function"></span>&#123;<br>Line L;<br>L.A = P2.y - P1.y;<br>L.B = P1.x - P2.x;<br>L.C = P2.x * P1.y - P1.x * P2.y;<br><span class="hljs-keyword">return</span> L;<br>&#125;<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><span id="一些函数"></span></p><h4 id="一些函数-1"><a href="#一些函数-1" class="headerlink" title="一些函数"></a>一些函数</h4><h5 id="判断点和直线的位置关系"><a href="#判断点和直线的位置关系" class="headerlink" title="判断点和直线的位置关系"></a>判断点和直线的位置关系</h5><p>还是利用向量积判断方向。<br>代码如下：</p><figure class="highlight cpp"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs cpp"><span class="hljs-comment">//1 在左侧 </span><br><span class="hljs-comment">//-1 在右侧 </span><br><span class="hljs-comment">//0 在直线上</span><br><span class="hljs-comment">//A, B:直线上点,P:待判断关系的点</span><br><span class="hljs-function"><span class="hljs-keyword">int</span> <span class="hljs-title">relation</span><span class="hljs-params">(Point A, Point B, Point P)</span></span><br><span class="hljs-function"></span>&#123;<br>    <span class="hljs-comment">// 1 left -1 right 0 in</span><br>    <span class="hljs-keyword">int</span> c = sgn(Cross((B - A), (P - A)));<br>    <span class="hljs-keyword">if</span>(c &lt; <span class="hljs-number">0</span>) <span class="hljs-keyword">return</span> <span class="hljs-number">1</span>;<br>    <span class="hljs-keyword">else</span> <span class="hljs-keyword">if</span>(c &gt; <span class="hljs-number">0</span>) <span class="hljs-keyword">return</span> <span class="hljs-number">-1</span>;<br>    <span class="hljs-keyword">return</span> <span class="hljs-number">0</span>;<br>&#125;<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h5 id="计算点到直线的距离"><a href="#计算点到直线的距离" class="headerlink" title="计算点到直线的距离"></a>计算点到直线的距离</h5><p>用向量比较好写。</p><figure class="highlight cpp"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs cpp"><span class="hljs-comment">//点到直线距离公式</span><br><span class="hljs-function"><span class="hljs-keyword">double</span> <span class="hljs-title">Distance_point_to_line</span><span class="hljs-params">(Point A, Point B, Point P)</span></span><br><span class="hljs-function"></span>&#123;<br>    Vector v1 = B - A, v2 = P - A;<br>    <span class="hljs-keyword">return</span> <span class="hljs-built_in">fabs</span>(Cross(v1, v2) / distance(v1));<span class="hljs-comment">//如果不取绝对值，那么得到的是有向距离</span><br>&#125;<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h5 id="计算两直线交点"><a href="#计算两直线交点" class="headerlink" title="计算两直线交点"></a>计算两直线交点</h5><p>在点向式意义下，两直线相交只需要判断它们的向量的向量积是否为0。</p><figure class="highlight cpp"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs cpp"><span class="hljs-comment">//一定要先判断Cross(v, w)是否为0</span><br><span class="hljs-comment">//A,v代表一条直线 B,w代表另一条直线</span><br><span class="hljs-function">Point <span class="hljs-title">Get_line_intersection</span><span class="hljs-params">(Point A,Vector v,Point B,Vector w)</span></span><br><span class="hljs-function"></span>&#123;<br>Vector u = A - B;<br><span class="hljs-keyword">double</span> t = Cross(w, u) / Cross(v, w);<br><span class="hljs-keyword">return</span> A + v * t;<br>&#125;<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h5 id="判断两线段是否相交"><a href="#判断两线段是否相交" class="headerlink" title="判断两线段是否相交"></a>判断两线段是否相交</h5><p>跨立实验和快速排斥实验</p><figure class="highlight cpp"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs cpp"><span class="hljs-function"><span class="hljs-keyword">bool</span> <span class="hljs-title">seg_cross_seg</span><span class="hljs-params">(Point a1, Point a2, Point b1, Point b2)</span></span><br><span class="hljs-function"></span>&#123;<br>    <span class="hljs-keyword">double</span> c1 = Cross(a2 - a1, b1 - a1), c2 = Cross(a2 - a1, b2 - a1);<br>    <span class="hljs-keyword">double</span> c3 = Cross(b2 - b1, a1 - b1), c4 = Cross(b2 - b1, a2 - b1);<br>    <br>    <span class="hljs-keyword">return</span>  (sgn(c1) * sgn(c2) &lt; <span class="hljs-number">0</span>) &amp;&amp;<br>            (sgn(c3) * sgn(c4) &lt; <span class="hljs-number">0</span>) &amp;&amp;<br>            min(a1.x,a2.x) &lt;= max(b1.x,b2.x) &amp;&amp;<br>            min(b1.x,b2.x) &lt;= max(a1.x,a2.x) &amp;&amp;<br>            min(a1.y,a2.y) &lt;= max(b1.y,b2.y) &amp;&amp;<br>            min(b1.y,b2.y) &lt;= max(a1.y,a2.y) ;<br>    <span class="hljs-comment">//如果算在端点处相交就改成 &lt;= 即可</span><br>&#125;<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h1 id="未完待续。。。"><a href="#未完待续。。。" class="headerlink" title="未完待续。。。"></a>未完待续。。。</h1>]]></content>
    
    
    
