    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h2 id="Today-is-lyx’s-first-day"><a href="#Today-is-lyx’s-first-day" class="headerlink" title="Today is lyx’s first day!"></a>Today is lyx’s first day!</h2><p>I will complete my work and Decorate my little home.</p><p>I would like to express my opinion and emotions.</p><p>There will be many sulotions to many problems.</p><p>And I Love U.</p>]]></content>
    
    
    
